org.opengis.cite.cdb10.util.reference

Class CdbReference

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.opengis.cite.cdb10.util.reference.CdbReference

  • public class CdbReference
extends Object
    Open the embedded CDB reference files so they may be used in validation tests. This class can be used to generate validator classes, which should be used in your test methods.
